This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with image and video super-resolution using convolutional neural networks. It could also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category as it deals with video processing. The paper also proposes a novel CNN architecture, which could fall under the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Finally, the paper involves optimization of computational complexity, which could fall under the Graphics (cs.GR) category.
